    "name": "The Lightkeeper Is Gone",
    "steam_appid": 3190760,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/0b956a6d4213081b5178f56da048a140.avif?t=1764875385\" width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>The Lightkeeper Is Gone</i> is a retro-stylized slow-burn horror adventure centered around a lighthouse keeper's mysterious disappearance</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Working on a lighthouse far away from civilization is a demanding job that takes a resilient spirit and iron discipline. The L—— Isle has only seen two keepers to date—and while the first managed well enough, the recent hire has turned out to be more of a nuisance. Their departure has left the light dark; someone must take their place. Will you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/f9e12b9271e6716f61d6a22e8b2a187b.poster.avif?t=1764875385\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/f9e12b9271e6716f61d6a22e8b2a187b.webm?t=1764875385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/f9e12b9271e6716f61d6a22e8b2a187b.mp4?t=1764875385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover the previous keeper's story piece by piece</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're given an explanation, but it seems underwhelming. Seek out clues, but be careful—not everything is as it seems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/31993bbfafa8ca91d85934f6d35e4cb1.poster.avif?t=1764875385\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/31993bbfafa8ca91d85934f6d35e4cb1.webm?t=1764875385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/31993bbfafa8ca91d85934f6d35e4cb1.mp4?t=1764875385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Look after the lighthouse</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've taken on a grave responsibility, and failing your duties will have consequences. The light must be started every evening—and make sure the lens stays clean!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/057a859ba46fbb63a252e8d7156b72e9.poster.avif?t=1764875385\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/057a859ba46fbb63a252e8d7156b72e9.webm?t=1764875385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/057a859ba46fbb63a252e8d7156b72e9.mp4?t=1764875385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take in the atmosphere</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Such a life is not for everyone, but you don't need anyone except for yourself. You will be given a lot of time to reflect upon your actions here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/067ba13ec5e4458889e15ef63ff92f1e.poster.avif?t=1764875385\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/067ba13ec5e4458889e15ef63ff92f1e.webm?t=1764875385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/067ba13ec5e4458889e15ef63ff92f1e.mp4?t=1764875385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Game's Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > several hours long choice-driven story told through the eyes of a new lighthouse keeper; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > multiple endings influenced by your actions; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > free exploration to uncover hidden details; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > engaging lighthouse maintenance mechanics inspired by real-world practices; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > an immersive, atmospheric world; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > a fishing mechanic.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
